    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>04402003000020</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>In view of the interpersonal relationship implied in the occurrence of ἀποσπάω in {S:04402003000020}, it would be possible to classify this meaning under the domain of Association (34).</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="2" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>04402100100012</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>It is possible to interpret ἀποσπάομαι in {S:04402100100012} as referring to the act of saying goodbye, and thus being equivalent to ἀποτάσσομαι[b] ({D:15.55}).</Content>
    </Note>
